Package org.example.scdpro2.ui.views.PackageDiagram

Class PackageRelationship<T extends javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane>

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
org.example.scdpro2.ui.views.PackageDiagram.PackageRelationship<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of package that the relationship connects, extending BorderPane.
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class PackageRelationship<T extends javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane> extends javafx.scene.Node
Represents a relationship between two packages in a diagram. Displays a connection between two packages using dotted lines and an arrow, along with draggable anchors and a relationship label.
